{"id": "1001526", "question": "Pandas怎样对dataframe中的一个时间列进行排序？", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>比如我的dataframe里有一列time</p><p>'2017-01-21 18:00:00', '2017-01-21 09:00:00','2017-01-21 15:00:00', '2017-01-21 12:00:00', '2017-01-21 13:00:00', '2017-01-21 14:00:00'</p><p>怎么让我的dataframe按照time时间先后顺序排列？</p><p><br/></p></div>", "viewer": 18122, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "时间序列", "Python"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>先把它转为时间对象</p><pre><code class=\"python\">df['time'] = pd.to_datetime(df['time'])</code></pre><p>然后再对time这列排序</p><pre><code class=\"python\">df.sort_values('time', inplace=True)</code></pre><p><br/></p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}]}